cs.LG, cs.DL, cs.SE, cs.DC, cs.CE 

The paper discusses a machine learning model repository and serving system with a focus on scientific applications. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.DL (Deep Learning). The paper also discusses the system's capabilities for reproducibility and scalability, which could fall under cs.SE (Software Engineering) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). Finally, the paper mentions early uses of the system for scientific applications, which could also fall under cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
